reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works great but smaller than expected
reviews.reviewText: Works well in my oven on air fry. It’s best if you only keep it to one layer of food or it won’t crisp evenly. The set is smaller than a cookie sheet size, I feel it’s a good value for the $.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pleased, but it does rust
reviews.reviewText: I like this very much. It serves it's purpose and it's very shiny. However, I'm noticing rust spots where the mesh wires connect. The bottom of the tray scratches easily and rust will form there too. I don't soak it in dishwater for long periods, so for being stainless steel, I'm leery for what the future holds.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Not as big as advertised
reviews.reviewText: I was expecting 13x9 pan as advertised. It is a bit smaller than that. I’ll keep it but not happy about it
